emuInput.TitMainTitle: Men and women wearing NAACP Pennsylvania State Conference tags seated at banquet tables in downtown YWCA for youth council luncheon meeting
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 31, 1959, pg. B2 reads: "Youth Council Delegates - Smiling faces shown above are those of representatives of 16 Youth Councils and college chapters of the State Conference at their luncheon meetings in the downtown YWCA."
